WEBVTT

00:00:29.043 --> 00:00:33.040
♪ On samo lebdi dalje Golgotom ♪

00:00:33.040 --> 00:00:34.690
♪ Gonjen svemoćnom hitnjom ♪

00:00:34.690 --> 00:00:37.662
♪ Avaj, mogla bi još uvek da ga stigne ♪

00:00:37.662 --> 00:00:39.626
♪ Kaži mi kuda ideš, Gospode ♪

00:00:39.626 --> 00:00:41.630
♪ I čemu ta žurba silna? ♪

00:00:41.630 --> 00:00:43.697
♪ Ta, ne smetaj mi, ženo ♪

00:00:43.697 --> 00:00:45.471
♪ Nemam da traćim vremena ♪

00:00:45.471 --> 00:00:49.439
♪ Jer brod isplovljava
u podne narednog dana ♪

00:00:49.439 --> 00:00:53.124
♪ I ja moram da budem tamo
u cik zore rane ♪

00:00:53.124 --> 00:00:55.292
♪ Ne smem da izostanem ♪

00:00:55.292 --> 00:00:57.110
♪ Posada očekuje mene ♪

00:00:57.110 --> 00:01:01.150
♪ Zarad čega bi drugog sami
Dobri Bog vaskrsao mene? ♪